config BR2_PKGSRC_PACKAGE_MAIL_CLAWS_MAIL_NOTIFICATION
	bool "claws-mail-notification-0.28nb1"
	help
	  Provides various ways to notify the user of new and unread email

	  The Notification plugin provides various ways to notify the user
	  of new and possibly unread mail. Currently, the following modules
	  are implemented:
	  
	  * A mail banner (stocks ticker-like widget)
	  * A popup window
