config BR2_PKGSRC_PACKAGE_MAIL_SYLPHEED
	bool "sylpheed-3.1.2nb1"
	help
	  Gtk based e-mail and netnews client

	  Sylpheed is an e-mail client (and news reader) based on GTK+ v2, running on
	  X Window System, and aiming for
	  
	  * Quick response
